Package lsystem.collection

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RuleList
    RuleList interface to a Collection of L-System rules
    StackInterface<E>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSList
    A storage class for context sensitive LSystem rules, accepts simple LSystem rules as well (however as yet stochastic rules are not accepted).
    PenStack
    A Pen tuned stack with minimal interface
    SimpleRuleList
    A storage class for non-stochastic rules
    StochasticList
    A storage class for weighted rules holds/implements the weighted selection logic (now as inner class since version 0.74 [24 November 2011-14])
    StochasticList.WeightedRuleChooser
    Inner class, to handle chooser logic
    TurtleStack
    A turtle tuned stack with minimal interface
